SELF INTRO:

Hello, my name is Abhinand, and I bring 8.9 years of total IT experience, including 4 years in Azure Data Engineering and 2 years in PySpark-based Big Data solutions.
I hold certifications as a Microsoft Certified Azure Data Engineer Associate and a Databricks Certified Associate Developer for Apache Spark, showcasing my dedication to mastering advanced data engineering tools and technologies.
My core expertise lies in designing and implementing scalable data pipelines and analytics solutions by leveraging both Azure cloud and big data technologies.
I have hands-on experience with tools such as Azure Data Factory, Azure Data Lake, Azure Databricks, Azure Synapse Analytics, and Power BI to build end-to-end pipelines and provide actionable insights for business decision-making. Additionally, I am proficient with technologies like PySpark, Apache Spark, Kafka, Hadoop, HDFS, Hive, Yarn, Impala, and HBase, which enable me to efficiently manage and process large-scale datasets.

In my Azure Data Engineering, I have:

Developed end-to-end ETL pipelines.
Implemented Data Lake Architecture with Medallion layers (Bronze, Silver, Gold).
Performed advanced data transformation and validation.
Delivered interactive visualizations using Power BI.

On the Big Data front, I have:

created data pipeline to extract file based data source from HDFS and transformed the data as per business needs using PySpark 
Monitored and Optimized PySpark jobs and workflows for enhanced performance.
Created Hive scripts for schema changes.

I am deeply passionate about crafting data-driven solutions that empower organizations to unlock insights, improve operations, and achieve their business objectives.
